Interoperability Test Report

This report was generated from the EXI interoperability test suite. The 3 tested implementations are EXIficient, OpenEXI and Canon. The table presents results for all combinations of decoder/encoder (e.g., the column labeled "Canon2OpenEXI" shows results for all test cases encoded by implementation "Canon" and decoded by implementation "OpenEXI"). At the time of writing OpenEXI does not support self-contained elements. That is the reason why one can see N/A entries in the table.

Note: The Working Group also maintains a list of publicly available implementations on its home page.

$Date Wed Dec 11 18:57:37 CET 2013
